Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:04:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使劲揉\N{\fs38}Manhandle them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大力不要停\N{\fs38}Give them the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好让它们爽一爽\N{\fs38}See if you can shuffle them. I mean, really get in there and knock them around.
