Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jessica\N{\fs38}Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来五分钟\N{\fs38}Five more minutes of this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就要生气了\N{\fs38}And I'm gonna get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.50,0:05:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jessica\N{\fs38}Je-jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jessica\N{\fs38}Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是我的错\N{\fs38}Not my fault this is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看呐\N{\fs38}Well, well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Frank 早上好\N{\fs38}Uh, morning, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"早上好" 你什么意思\N{\fs38}"Morning"? What was what is that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在取笑我吗\N{\fs38}You making fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是在暗示我家里穷吗\N{\fs38}Are you trying to say my family's poor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Frank  没必要动刀子吧\N{\fs38}Oh, geez, frank. I don't know if a knife is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用刀子也能搞定啊\N{\fs38}I mean, you know, y-you kind of had things handled without it.
