Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这你就错了 Morty\N{\fs38}Big mistake, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我要砍了你 因为我家有钱\N{\fs38}And now I'm gonna cut you, 'cause my family's rich.
