Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\fs38}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去另外一个次元办点事儿\N{\fs38}I got an errand to run in a whole different dimension.
