Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 Rick 你把Frank咋了 \N{\fs38}Oh, geez, Rick. W-what'd you do to frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很明显啊Morty 我把他冻住了\N{\fs38}It's pretty obvious, Morty. I froze him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你帮忙\N{\fs38}Now listen. I need your help, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赶紧离离离开这儿\N{\fs38}I mean, we got we got to get get the hell out of here
