Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很重要 快来 Morty\N{\fs38}It's important. Come on, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道 Rick\N{\fs38}I don't know, rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再逃学了\N{\fs38}I-I can't leave school again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道去那边有多危险吗\N{\fs38}Do you have any concept of how much higher the stakes get out there, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我一个人能行吗\N{\fs38}What do you think? I can just do it all by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来\N{\fs38}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs38}Aw, geez. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或许可以翘一节历史\N{\fs38}I guess I can skip history.
