Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是该给他解冻\N{\fs38}I mean, shouldn't you unfreeze him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等会儿再说 \N{\fs38}I'll do it later, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没事的\N{\fs38}He'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\fs38}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天 我要遇上Frank Palicky了\N{\fs38}Oh, my god. I'm about to walk past frank Palicky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是以后讲给我们孩子听的邂逅啊\N{\fs38}This is the story we'll be telling our children.
