Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给\N{\fs38}Scalpel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咚咚咚\N{\fs38}Knock, knock.
