Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 请务必告诉我你有非来不可的理由\N{\fs38}Jerry, please tell me you're here for an incredibly urgent reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午餐啊\N{\fs38}Well, it's lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数千年来的三餐之一啊\N{\fs38}I mean, it's one of three meals that have existed for millennia.
