Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说啥\N{\fs38}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 这个问题咱别再吵了\N{\fs38}Okay. Let's not rehash that fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白你很忙 我这就走\N{\fs38}I sense that you're busy and will now be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哦\N{\fs38}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地上这是啥呀\N{\fs38}What is this on the floor?
