Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tom 我知道它快不行了\N{\fs38}Hey, Tom. We know when we're losing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这哔哔叫我听得见\N{\fs38}We can hear the beeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 来吧 Morty 我们走\N{\fs38}There she is. All right. Come on, Morty. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs38}Oh, geez. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 Rick\N{\fs38}Oh, man, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个啥地方\N{\fs38}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是35c次元 这儿的气候非常适合一种特殊的树\N{\fs38}It's dimension 35c, and it's got the perfect climate conditions for a special type of
