Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树上有果子 果子里有种子\N{\fs38}And there's fruit in those trees, and there's seeds in those fruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是奇异种\N{\fs38}I'm talking about mega seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:08:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种种子非常强大 我的研究需要这些种子\N{\fs38}They're they're incredibly powerful, and I need them to help me with my research, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 我看了下四周\N{\fs38}Oh, man, Rick. I'm looking around this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有点怕怕的呢\N{\fs38}And I'm starting to work up some anxiety about this whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧好吧\N{\fs38}All right. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点 听我说 Morty\N{\fs38}Calm down. Listen to me, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道人在新环境里会感到不安\N{\fs38}I know that new situations can be intimidating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看周围 又吓人又陌生\N{\fs38}You're looking around, and it's all scary and different, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迎头而上 像一头公牛一样冲过去\N{\fs38}You know, m-meeting them head on, charging right into them like a bull
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.48,0:08:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样人才能成长\N{\fs38}that's how we grow as people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我经常遇到可怕的事\N{\fs38}I'm no stranger to scary situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在和它们打交道\N{\fs38}I deal with them all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.29,0:08:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟着我\N{\fs38}Now, if you just stick with me, Morty,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.07,0:08:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定会 妈呀 快跑 Morty\N{\fs38}we're gonna be... Holy crap, Morty, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这辈子都没见过这玩意儿\N{\fs38}I never seen that thing before in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是啥鬼东西啊\N{\fs38}I don't even know what the hell it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑啊Morty\N{\fs38}We got to get out of here, morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会杀了我们的\N{\fs38}It's gonna kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要挂了\N{\fs38}We're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要挂了\N{\fs38}We're gonna die, morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.71,0:08:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 深呼吸\N{\fs38}Oh, Morty, take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸点新鲜空气\N{\fs38}Breathe that, breathe that fresh air in, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闻到没\N{\fs38}Y-you smell that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充满了冒险气息啊 Morty\N{\fs38}That's the smell of adventure, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一条完全不同的进化之路的味道\N{\fs38}That's that's the smell of of of of a whole different evolutionary timeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了Rick\N{\fs38}All right, Rick,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要多久啊 \N{\fs38}Look how much longer is this gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不是该回学校了\N{\fs38}Shouldn't I be back at school by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑\N{\fs38}Are you joking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你周围这些鬼玩意儿\N{\fs38}I mean, look at all the crazy crap surrounding us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那边那个\N{\fs38}Look at that thing right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么鬼\N{\fs38}W-what the hell is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:08:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得你在学校能看见\N{\fs38}You think you're gonna see that kind of thing at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:08:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看它滚来滚去\N{\fs38}Look at it just lumbering around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法用逻辑理解\N{\fs38}It defies all logic that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 我明白\N{\fs38}Yeah, Rick, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们周围全是怪物\N{\fs38}We're surrounded by monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才想走啊\N{\fs38}That's kind of the reason why I want to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见了吗 Morty\N{\fs38}Ta-ta-ta-ta-ta-ta. Morty, you see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见下面是什么了吗\N{\fs38}You see what we just stumbled upon, morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道是啥吗\N{\fs38}Any idea what that is down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇异树吗\N{\fs38}The mega trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错Morty\N{\fs38}That's right, Morty
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长着果子的奇异树\N{\fs38}The mega trees with the mega fruit on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要的就是这个呀 Morty 种子就在那儿\N{\fs38}And that's what I'm talking about, morty. That's where my seeds are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们按你说的来 那就永远找不到了\N{\fs38}If we would have done what you wanted, I would have never have
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你如此迷恋你的学校\N{\fs38}Found them, because y because you're so in love with school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 好吧\N{\fs38}All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些种子到底有什么特别的\N{\fs38}So, what's so special about these seeds, anyways?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 别问这么多问题\N{\fs38}You ask a lot of questions, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不好\N{\fs38}Not very charismatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.49,0:09:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很碍事的\N{\fs38}It makes you kind of an under underfoot figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上这鞋子 Morty\N{\fs38}Just take these shoes, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是特制的吸附鞋\N{\fs38}They're sp special grappling shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要穿着这宝贝儿\N{\fs38}When you're wearing these things ba these babies,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想往哪儿走往哪儿走\N{\fs38}You can basically just walk on any surface you want, Morty
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往上 往下 倒立 转到左边\N{\fs38}Up, down, below, turn around to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么都行\N{\fs38}These things really bring it all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊\N{\fs38}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 你得先启动它们 \N{\fs38}You have to turn them on, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把鞋子的开关打开\N{\fs38}The shoes have to be turned on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会送我爸去养老院\N{\fs38}I am not putting my father in a home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才刚回到我的生活中\N{\fs38}He just came back into my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:10:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就想这么把他塞床垫下面\N{\fs38}And you want to grab him and stuff him under a mattress
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟上月的维多利亚的秘密产品目录为伍吗\N{\fs38}like last month's victoria's secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了我是在给你订情人节礼物嘛\N{\fs38}I told you I was ordering you something for valentine's day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你爸对我们的孩子有很不好的影响\N{\fs38}More importantly, your father is a horrible influence on our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没问题吧 Beth\N{\fs38}Everything cool in here, Beth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 Davin\N{\fs38}It's fine, Davin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好\N{\fs38}Okay, cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们今天一起完成了一件伟大的事\N{\fs38}You know, we did something great today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么比马儿的心脏更高贵自由了\N{\fs38}There's nothing more noble and free than the heart of a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然我们在吵架\N{\fs38}Since we're fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你跟那家伙有过什么\N{\fs38}If you ever have an affair with that guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.23,0:10:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就去酒店房间吞子弹\N{\fs38}I will come to the hotel room and blow my brains out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把脑浆全崩到你的裸体上\N{\fs38}all over your naked bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解你承受的压力\N{\fs38}Look, I appreciate the stress you're under,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是Morty早在我爸搬进来前\N{\fs38}but morty was having trouble in school way
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学习就有问题了\N{\fs38}Before my dad moved in,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我唯一能看到Rick带来的影响就是 这么久以来\N{\fs38}and the only influence I can see rick having is that, for the first time in his life,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty第一次有了朋友\N{\fs38}Morty has a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你是对的\N{\fs38}Well, maybe you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是吧\N{\fs38}Uh, yeah, maybe I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是我爸的女儿\N{\fs38}I'm my father's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很聪明\N{\fs38}I'm smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然咋当上心外科医生的\N{\fs38}Why do you think I'm a heart surgeon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马心外科医生\N{\fs38}Horse heart surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs38}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Smith太太吗\N{\fs38}Mrs. Smith?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.20,0:10:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是阴道校长 别做联想 \N{\fs38}This is principal Vagina no relation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问你和Morty的父亲今天下午能\N{\fs38}I wonder if you and morty's father might be able to have a
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来谈谈吗\N{\fs38}Chat with me this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty你把你的腿弄得真惨\N{\fs38}Morty, oh, you really d-did a number on your legs right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得把开关打开 这鞋子才能用啊\N{\fs38}You know, you got to turn the shoes on, morty, for them to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的打开了\N{\fs38}Yeah, look I turned mine on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下来的多顺当\N{\fs38}I had no problem getting down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直是轻松愉快\N{\fs38}It was a leisurely breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快疼死了 Rick\N{\fs38}I'm in a lot of pain, rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.61,0:11:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我看得出来\N{\fs38}Yeah, I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你应该还能帮我把种子采来的吧\N{\fs38}But do you think you'll still be able to help me collect my seeds, morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑\N{\fs38}Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 Rick\N{\fs38}That's it, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忍不了了\N{\fs38}That's the last straw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.48,0:11:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直不敢相信\N{\fs38}I can't believe this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我两条腿都断了\N{\fs38}I'm sitting here with both of my legs broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还要我去帮你弄种子\N{\fs38}and you're still asking me about getting those seeds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗷嗷嗷\N{\fs38}Ooh! Ow! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个怪物\N{\fs38}Y-y-you're a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟希特勒似的 至少希特勒心里还装着德国\N{\fs38}Y-you're like hitler, but but even hitler cared about Germany or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.59,0:11:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 等我一下 Morty\N{\fs38}Okay, hold on just a second, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哦Rick 这个一下就治好了我的腿\N{\fs38}Wow, Rick. That stuff just healed my broken legs instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这辈子没觉得这么好过\N{\fs38}I mean, I've never felt so good in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs38}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管了 Morty\N{\fs38}Don't worry about it, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快过来帮我弄种子\N{\fs38}Just come help me get these seeds, all right, buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 Rick\N{\fs38}Sure thing, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你没问\N{\fs38}Not that you asked,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过刚才我去了一个未来的次元\N{\fs38}Morty, but what just happened there is I went into a future
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医学高度发达\N{\fs38}Dimension with such advanced medicine
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治断腿的血清到处的药店都有卖的\N{\fs38}that they had broken-leg serum at every corner drugstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西满街都是\N{\fs38}The stuff was all over the place, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听上去好厉害啊 Rick\N{\fs38}Wow, that's pretty crazy, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是有个小问题 \N{\fs38}There's just one problem, Morty, one little hang-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去的次元太发达了\N{\fs38}The dimension I visited was so advanced,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们抑制了衰老\N{\fs38}they had also halted the aging process,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那儿的每个人都很年轻 也从未老过\N{\fs38}and everyone there was young, morty, and they had been forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是那儿唯一的老人\N{\fs38}I was the only old person there, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那儿 我就像一个名人般\N{\fs38}It was like I was some sort of, you know, celebrity, walking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们觉得我可迷人了\N{\fs38}I-I was fascinating to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边有很多美女\N{\fs38}There were a lot of attractive Women there, morty,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们都想和我共度良宵\N{\fs38}and they they they they all wanted time with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和很多美女玩得非常开心 \N{\fs38}I had a lot of fun with a lot of young ladies,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我在那边待太久了 次元传送装置它\N{\fs38}but I spent so much time there, my interdimensional portal device
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有能量了\N{\fs38}it's got no charge left, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有能量了\N{\fs38}It's got no charge left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥\N{\fs38}What?!
